summary: So fun pokemon fact Articuno, the ice type legendary. It’s japanese name is フリーザー Which is pronounced furīzā, which 100% means...
body:
So fun pokemon fact

Articuno, the ice type legendary. It’s japanese name is フリーザー
Which is pronounced furīzā, which 100% means they called their legendary pokemon freezer. I love that.

“But what about the others?” I hear you ask.

Moltres = ファイヤー = faiyā = fire

Zapdos is sandā which is less fun but like

OMG the legendary birds! Sander, Fire and Freezer!

I can’t..
